            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Juggernauts protect locations dedicated to a particular faith, their massive forms infused with divine energy that animates them and infuses them with their deity\u2019s power. Some faiths use a juggernaut as a mobile shrine, anointing it with sacred materials and offering prayers to the divine."
        }
    ],
